{"tid":1295934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港振作】各位，化療電療係好辛苦，但係絕對比起任由癌症擴散舒服","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T15:27:09.000Z","uid":131691,"like":132,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b22b074b4e7e9fddd9cc7d6bde54501b3f3001e7","tid":1295934,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位，香港病咗</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而我哋香港人，就係解藥</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由北面傳入嘅共產政權<br />\n已經令到香港政府病入膏肓<br />\n至今，行政、立法、執法相繼倒下<br />\n僅存嘅司法，亦搖搖欲墜<br />\n<br />\n一條送中條例，揭起咗香港歷史上最重要嘅一役<br />\n多年累積嘅腐敗，今次一次過爆哂出嚟<br />\n多年醞釀嘅經驗，亦同時間喺今次抗爭爆發<br />\n<br />\n一個癌症病人，接受電療，化療，鏢靶藥，固然係辛苦<br />\n脫髮，消瘦，甚至最後依然係死亡<br />\n<strong>但係唔接受治療，就一定死</strong><br />\n<strong>所以前面路途幾咁艱鉅，幾咁恐怖<br />\n我哋香港人都要繼續醫治屬於我哋嘅香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n各位，我哋處於香港歷史嘅轉捩點<br />\n香港嘅未來，就係靠大家<br />\n<br />\n7月7號標記住香港執法機關已經成爲見人就打嘅流氓<br />\n一班社會寄生蟲，指示一班社會渣宰，去蠶食屬於我哋嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n未來嘅恐怖只會越嚟越厲害<br />\n你準備好未？<br />\n<br />\n你會爲屬於你嘅香港付出一切嗎？"},{"pid":"691bd1e43f69392178fb52736f4232f138fa1f5a","tid":1295934,"uid":131691,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"仲有一日，大家就已經做咗成個月同路人啦<br />\n各位香港兒女，多謝你哋每人至今嘅付出<br />\n前路一定會黑暗，但係我唔怕！<br />\n因爲！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋係香港人！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a650c573578f07192b68b3cccfc36d4891b18838","tid":1295934,"uid":131691,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"b0c400d57a16851942532c5d320b489da7793dce","tid":1295934,"uid":52793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"樓主呢個比喻唔錯"},{"pid":"e2fabed0633e46b3aa18b251fc07b4793b244711","tid":1295934,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"Yes 仲有一絲希望都要堅持落去，希望香港快D好返"},{"pid":"c6ddc0d7330499a6fe38f7545a7d3ae21d0c0932","tid":1295934,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"保持團結，唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b3f288aebf993232c4bd1813b551ade2504ec6","tid":1295934,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2fabed0633e46b3aa18b251fc07b4793b244711","tid":1295934,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"Yes 仲有一絲希望都要堅持落去，希望香港快D好返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"就算看似冇希望，都要製造新嘅希望出嚟<br />\n大家都係香港人，有咩好怕！"},{"pid":"c5c65cd93bda1d3015f19a014c2c9e6d246e0588","tid":1295934,"uid":269472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"Whatever it takes ! <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOz46Gx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOz46Gx.png&h=fb3f2ed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93645538af0b138ad1380cb763e67f7be3fd107a","tid":1295934,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"我同你諗法有啲唔同<br />\n覺得香港人係白血球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過癌症唔係最新免疫療法咩<br />\n可能我哋都係等緊一個突破點<br />\n<br />\n科技突破最有可能幫到我哋<br />\n其他可能性低啲"},{"pid":"613fde66c944a9aa90a29daf26eccdc1e1ba2796","tid":1295934,"uid":129054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"132e9ec0e9935fa1a53f4e49c25aaebe45d2e039","tid":1295934,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ddc0d7330499a6fe38f7545a7d3ae21d0c0932","tid":1295934,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"保持團結，唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"